# Magic SMS Data Policy

## 1. Data Collection
### Categories Processed:
- Account registration data
- Message content and metadata
- Device information

## 2. Legal Basis
### Processing Grounds:
- Article 6(1)(b) GDPR (contractual necessity)
- Section 120(c) CCPA (business purposes)

## 3. Data Subject Rights
### User Options:
- Access requests via support@magicsms.com
- Erasure limited by retention schedule

## 4. Law Enforcement
### Request Requirements:
- Valid jurisdiction
- Properly executed warrant/subpoena
- Submit to legal@magicsms.com
